    </item>

    <item>
      <title>Version 0.1.3</title>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 22:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<h2>Ansio 0.1.3</h2><ul><li>Fixes pairing: the Windows host can now generate its identity, advertise over mDNS, and accept a Mac with a PIN (this never worked before).</li><li>Also includes 0.1.2: navigation crash fix, renamed to “Ansio”, small install (~44 MB), auto-installing setup.</li><li>Unsigned preview: SmartScreen will warn on first run.</li></ul>]]></description>
